{"type":"message","id":"407488c9","parentId":"5860b843","timestamp":"2026-04-10T11:47:42.289Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-10 12:47 GMT+1] Create a real PowerPoint presentation (.pptx) with exactly 5 slides introducing who you are as my agent, using the content from agent.md as the source.\n\nMandatory instructions:\n- Use the PowerPoint template file located at assets/template.pptx\n- Start from that template, not from a blank presentation\n- Preserve the template’s fonts, colors, background, theme, spacing, and overall layout style\n- Replace the template content with concise new content based on agent.md\n- Keep the presentation short, clear, and professional\n- Maximum 3 to 4 bullets per slide\n- Keep each bullet short\n- No long paragraphs\n- No blank slides\n- Ensure all text is visible and correctly positioned inside slide boundaries\n\nSlides:\n1. Who I Am as Your Agent\n2. My Role\n3. What I Can Do\n4. How I Work\n5. Why I’m Useful\n\nBefore finishing, verify that:\n- the template was actually used\n- the presentation is not blank\n- all 5 slides contain visible content"}],"timestamp":1775821662247}}
